<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-11922] BatchlogManagerTest is failing intermittently</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-11922</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;BatchlogManagerTest&lt;/tt&gt; is failing sometimes with the following trace:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;    [junit] Testcase: testLegacyReplay(org.apache.cassandra.batchlog.BatchlogManagerTest):      FAILED
    [junit] [BigTableReader(path=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;/Users/oleksandrpetrov/foss/java/cassandra/build/test/cassandra/data:0/system/batches-919a4bc57a333573b03e13fc3f68b465/mb-2-big-Data.db&apos;&lt;/span&gt;), BigTableReader(path=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;/Users/oleksandrpetrov/foss/java/cassandra/build/test/cassandra/data:0/system/batches-919a4bc57a333573b03e13fc3f68b465/mb-1-big-Data.db&apos;&lt;/span&gt;)]
    [junit] junit.framework.AssertionFailedError: [BigTableReader(path=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;/Users/oleksandrpetrov/foss/java/cassandra/build/test/cassandra/data:0/system/batches-919a4bc57a333573b03e13fc3f68b465/mb-2-big-Data.db&apos;&lt;/span&gt;), BigTableReader(path=&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;/Users/oleksandrpetrov/foss/java/cassandra/build/test/cassandra/data:0/system/batches-919a4bc57a333573b03e13fc3f68b465/mb-1-big-Data.db&apos;&lt;/span&gt;)]
    [junit]     at org.apache.cassandra.db.ColumnFamilyStore.discardSSTables(ColumnFamilyStore.java:2521)
    [junit]     at org.apache.cassandra.db.ColumnFamilyStore$6.run(ColumnFamilyStore.java:2155)
    [junit]     at java.util.concurrent.Executors$RunnableAdapter.call(Executors.java:511)
    [junit]     at org.apache.cassandra.db.ColumnFamilyStore.runWithCompactionsDisabled(ColumnFamilyStore.java:2224)
    [junit]     at org.apache.cassandra.db.ColumnFamilyStore.truncateBlocking(ColumnFamilyStore.java:2166)
    [junit]     at org.apache.cassandra.batchlog.BatchlogManagerTest.setUp(BatchlogManagerTest.java:100)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Sometimes there are running compactions despite the fact they should have been waited upon before truncate. &lt;tt&gt;pause&lt;/tt&gt; and &lt;tt&gt;resume&lt;/tt&gt; are called on the &lt;tt&gt;CompactionStrategyManager&lt;/tt&gt; appropriately.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
